description: Red Wagon Creamery serves artisan ice cream that follows the seasons, using locally-sourced and organic ingredients to make the most amazing ice cream you've ever tried, all out of an adorable red cart. Flavors range from Wandering Goat Coffee to Hail to the Bee!, each more delicious than the last. Stop by at your next festival, or bring them out to your next big event!
name: Red Wagon Creamery
